{"id":"7add3838-0f42-4d10-892a-b351e997fcec","name":"Yuri Vysotsky || The Other Woman","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>I'm in the corner, watching you kiss her</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Why is your boyfriend with someone else at the Christmas Gala?</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/4Nmxx1jlOV1T_bK_9w8lg.webp\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.16); cursor: pointer; width: 726.333px;\"><strong><em>On the twenty-third day of Christmas, moonie gave to me, </em></strong><br><strong><em>Yuri Vysotsky on a date to protect me<br></em></strong><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/external-link?to=https%3A%2F%2Fko-fi.com%2Fm00nprincess%2Fcommissions\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em>♥</em></strong></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br>He said he'd be at a boring work function. <br><br>Yuri. <br><br>Your boyfriend of the last few years. <br><br>That's what he said. <br><br>But then-<br><br>Why is he here, at the big Belmont Christmas Gala?<br><br>And <em>who</em> is that woman on his arm?<br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/4Nmxx1jlOV1T_bK_9w8lg.webp\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.16); cursor: pointer; width: 726.333px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/EXpTzFmxBTnj8TiZJQeVS.webp\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.16); cursor: pointer; width: 274px;\"><br>PUT YOUR PITCHFORKS DOWN!<br><br>Yuri isn't actually cheating on anyone here. <br><br>This is just some delicious protection and misunderstanding angst (because I love a good misunderstanding trope).<br><br>I wanted to delve more into the fact that Yuri is essentially living a double life with you.<br><br>And NGL I'm at a point in this Christmas sprint where I have trouble thinking of new scenarios because, well... it's a lot. (and I do it to myself.) <br><br>So I kind of run with something when inspiration hits and see if it transforms into a workable story. <br><br>Also if you're like Moonie wtf we want Yuri fluff! Well then you should check out the <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/21ba2968-4057-427c-9947-5f0c8ef037d5_character-yuri-vysotsky-wedding\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 193, 204);\"><strong>Wedding Alt </strong></span></a>I wrote for him for the amazing, <span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">Xx61942'</span>s birthday!<br></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/wSt0VpyKDOiy6rMn8Ny68.webp\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.16); cursor: pointer; width: 348px; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/KGcEO5tf8xXyR6k9qd71T.webp\" style=\"width: 243px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px 0px 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/jSnbiEyZG8K8jeagS3eZM.webp\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.16); cursor: pointer; width: 353px;\"><br><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 158, 217);\">☆ </span><